#

Hearty Lentil Soup

55 min
$12.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegangluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

main

Tags:

souphealthyvegetarian

Description

A comforting and nutritious lentil soup packed with vegetables and flavor, perfect for any day of the week.

Ingredients

  • green or brown lentils: 1 cup
  • carrots, diced: 2
  • celery stalks, diced: 2
  • onion, chopped: 1
  • garlic cloves, minced: 2
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • parsley, chopped (for garnish): optional
